import "bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
import "bootstrap"

import { createApp } from 'vue'

import { createRouter, createWebHistory } from 'vue-router'

import App from './App.vue'

import InicioPage from '@/pages/InicioPage.vue'
import HotelesVer from '@/pages/HotelesVer.vue'
import HotelesCrear from '@/pages/HotelesCrear.vue'
import HabitacionesTipo from '@/pages/HabitacionesTipo.vue'
import Acomodaciones from '@/pages/Acomodaciones.vue'


const router = createRouter({
    history: createWebHistory(),
    routes: [
        {patch: '/', name:'InicioPage', component: InicioPage},
        {patch: '/HotelesCrear', name:'HotelesCrear', component: HotelesCrear},
        {patch: '/HotelesVer', name:'HoHotelesVerme', component: HotelesVer},
        {patch: '/HabitacionesTipo', name:'HabitacionesTipo', component: HabitacionesTipo},
        {patch: '/Acomodaciones', name:'Acomodaciones', component: Acomodaciones},
    ]
})


createApp(App)
.use(router)
.mount('#app')
